    "Energy Efficiency.",
    "Our FinTral models, similar to many large language models (LLMs), required significant training time and computational resources, and thus are not particularly energy efficient.",
    "We acknowledge this as a critical issue and advocate for ongoing research into developing more energyefficient models.",
    "Our pretraining datasets are collected from public domains, encompassing a wide range of financial topics and sources.",
